{"name":"Mathlib.Tactic.IrreducibleDef","instances":[],"imports":["Init","Lean"],"declarations":[{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/IrreducibleDef.lean#L68-L74","name":"Lean.Elab.Command.command_Irreducible_def___","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/IrreducibleDef.html#Lean.Elab.Command.command_Irreducible_def___","doc":"Introduces an irreducible definition.\n`irreducible_def foo := 42` generates\na constant `foo : Nat` as well as\na theorem `foo_def : foo = 42`.\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/IrreducibleDef.lean#L56-L61","name":"Lean.Elab.Command.commandStop_at_first_error_","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/IrreducibleDef.html#Lean.Elab.Command.commandStop_at_first_error_","doc":"Executes the commands,\nand stops after the first error.\nIn short, S-A-F-E.\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/IrreducibleDef.lean#L51-L52","name":"Lean.Elab.Command.termValue_proj_","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/IrreducibleDef.html#Lean.Elab.Command.termValue_proj_","doc":"`value_proj x` elabs to `@x.value` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/IrreducibleDef.lean#L42-L42","name":"Lean.Elab.Command.termEta_helper_","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/IrreducibleDef.html#Lean.Elab.Command.termEta_helper_","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/876d9cc42ccbfea023752e40e6edb7279d9c6b5a/Mathlib/Tactic/IrreducibleDef.lean#L33-L34","name":"Lean.Elab.Command.«termDelta%_»","docLink":"./Mathlib/Tactic/IrreducibleDef.html#Lean.Elab.Command.«termDelta%_»","doc":"`delta% t` elaborates to a head-delta reduced version of `t`. "}]}